Class IMSController

java.lang.Object
com.example.ims_app.IMSController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class IMSController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The Main Modal View Controller which handles event and execution logic. Handles redirects to other fxml views as well.

      protected void onDeletePartsButtonClick(javafx.event.ActionEvent e)
      Event handler/listener that fires from the delete parts button and opens a confirmation alertbox. On confirmation, it deletes the selected product on the table or throws an exception on unexpected failure.
      Parameters:
      e - Pre-generated and auto-handled event argument.

    • onDeleteProductsButtonClick

      protected void onDeleteProductsButtonClick(javafx.event.ActionEvent e)
      Event handler/listener that fires from the delete products button and opens a confirmation alertbox. On confirmation, it deletes the selected product on the table or throws an exception on unexpected failure. If the user attempts to delete a product with any associated parts, a popup error alertbox will display and prevent the deletion of the product.
      Parameters:
      e - Pre-generated and auto-handled event argument.
